1
00:00:06,010 --> 00:00:08,430
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,430 --> 00:00:12,090
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,090 --> 00:00:18,280
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,280 --> 00:00:24,500
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:30,730
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,730 --> 00:00:35,910
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:35,910 --> 00:00:43,010
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,010 --> 00:00:48,240
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,850
♫ Be your light ♫

10
00:00:49,850 --> 00:00:55,310
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,310 --> 00:01:02,010
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,010 --> 00:01:08,680
♫ With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:11,799
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:15,100
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

15
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:18,680
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

16
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:22,799
Three, two, three, four, five, six, seven, done.

17
00:01:22,799 --> 00:01:26,300
How's that, Meng? Did I do it right this time?

18
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:28,740
Beibei, not entirely right.

19
00:01:28,740 --> 00:01:32,859
Look, this part should go like this.

20
00:01:32,859 --> 00:01:34,679
Like this.

21
00:01:34,679 --> 00:01:37,299
Even I know it now. Look.

22
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:44,239
Gao Yang, it's just a cheerleading team.

23
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:46,920
She doesn't have to try so hard, right?

24
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,340
The cheerleading team is very important.

25
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,719
Why?

26
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:53,580
It's the first time you and Mi Jia are participating in a major competition.

27
00:01:53,580 --> 00:01:55,940
When you're speeding up right before the finish line,

28
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:58,799
what if you see Niu Wanwan and bam, you lost your first place?

29
00:01:58,799 --> 00:02:00,680
That's an overstatement.

30
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:04,119
Anyway, we can't let Niu Wanwan be the lead.

31
00:02:04,119 --> 00:02:05,759
- Do it yourself.
- Why?

32
00:02:05,759 --> 00:02:08,779
Beibei, why don't you drink some water?

33
00:02:08,779 --> 00:02:11,740
We're running out of time. I'm in no mood for water.

34
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:13,439
You and Xiaowen are about to compete.

35
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:18,240
I have to beat that Niu Wanwan in terms of vigor and spirit!

36
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:21,420
W-We appreciate y-your intention.

37
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:24,319
But i-in all fairness,

38
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:27,080
Niu Wanwan i-is really a better dancer than you.

39
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:29,860
Exactly. You're just a bad copy of her.

40
00:02:29,860 --> 00:02:32,540
I'm a bad copy of you!

41
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:34,800
No. You're doing a pretty good job.

42
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:38,400
You see, Niu Wanwan learned to dance when she was a child.

43
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,660
- Did you learn to dance?
- No.

44
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,060
You never learned it.

45
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:45,479
That's why you can't compare your shortcoming with her strength, right?

46
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:47,680
Yes. Look at that.

47
00:02:47,680 --> 00:02:51,020
That's called eloquence. Listen carefully, you two.

48
00:02:51,020 --> 00:02:52,919
I have my own strength too!

49
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:58,059
My strength is... never giving up!

50
00:02:58,059 --> 00:02:59,659
Beibei.

51
00:03:00,379 --> 00:03:01,939
Go for it!

52
00:03:01,939 --> 00:03:03,739
Go for it!

53
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:08,359
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight. Two, two, three, four...

54
00:03:08,359 --> 00:03:14,240
But Beibei isn't talented in this aspect. Maybe we shouldn't push her.

55
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,860
But no one else from our class can do it.

56
00:03:16,860 --> 00:03:19,239
- Yes, there is.
- Who?

57
00:03:19,239 --> 00:03:21,460
- You.
- Are you crazy?

58
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:25,240
You said it yourself that you'll be waiting for me by the finish line.

59
00:03:25,240 --> 00:03:29,520
But cheerleaders are all girls. How could a man like me do that?

60
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:32,460
Jin Beibei wants to compete with me for the lead.

61
00:03:32,460 --> 00:03:34,519
She even uses the same arm and leg when she walks.

62
00:03:36,580 --> 00:03:38,380
Dawei,

63
00:03:43,059 --> 00:03:47,399
I don't have time lately. Don't come to me for tutoring.

64
00:03:47,399 --> 00:03:51,379
It's all right if you're busy. I can just learn on my own.

65
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:55,960
By the way, here's your book.

66
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,580
Thank you for tutoring me before.

67
00:04:02,580 --> 00:04:06,560
It's all right. I just did what the teacher told me to do.

68
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,180
But you should reflect on yourself.

69
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:11,280
The college entrance exam is around the corner and you're still making up for Sophomore classes.

70
00:04:11,280 --> 00:04:12,959
You're right.

71
00:04:14,059 --> 00:04:15,659
Wait a minute.

72
00:04:16,620 --> 00:04:20,620
Dawei, you used to be an athlete, right?

73
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:24,479
I used to be a goalkeeper.

74
00:04:24,479 --> 00:04:28,060
What gift do you want before your game each time?

75
00:04:28,360 --> 00:04:29,920
Well...

76
00:04:29,920 --> 00:04:32,160
I... I'm not longer in the team.

77
00:04:35,339 --> 00:04:39,039
Forget it. I'm leaving.

78
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:49,679
Dawei, what gift do you want?

79
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:02,479
Xiaowen, I'll cheer you on during your competition.

80
00:05:03,779 --> 00:05:05,900
Isn't that Ye Xiaowen?

81
00:05:10,460 --> 00:05:14,260
- Dawei, should we beat him up?
- Don't cause me any trouble.

82
00:05:16,940 --> 00:05:20,639
Is there anything you like?

83
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:40,219
Go, Xiaowen!

84
00:05:58,660 --> 00:06:02,240
[Episode 13: Looking Forward to Your Future]

85
00:06:07,460 --> 00:06:10,259
Old Jin, be honest, are you having another one?

86
00:06:10,259 --> 00:06:11,219
Another what?

87
00:06:11,219 --> 00:06:12,539
A third child.

88
00:06:12,539 --> 00:06:14,139
What third child?

89
00:06:14,139 --> 00:06:16,779
Jin Beibei, Jin Doudou, Jin Baobao.

90
00:06:16,779 --> 00:06:20,460
Doudou already told me that your wife is pregnant again.

91
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:23,200
Bin, I asked you to babysit.

92
00:06:23,200 --> 00:06:24,820
Why are you asking so many questions?

93
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:26,420
Then why did you go to the hospital?

94
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,580
For a health exam!

95
00:06:28,580 --> 00:06:30,979
You had a health exam? Are you all right?

96
00:06:30,979 --> 00:06:33,599
I'm fine. It's just...

97
00:06:33,599 --> 00:06:35,779
a small heart problem.

98
00:06:35,779 --> 00:06:37,139
Then you should take care of yourself.

99
00:06:37,139 --> 00:06:38,939
I know.

100
00:06:41,060 --> 00:06:42,659
You have nothing else to do?

101
00:06:42,659 --> 00:06:44,319
Why are you still standing here?

102
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:46,800
I'll go work on the track and field team.

103
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,739
Hurry up!

104
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:59,619
Old Jin, as a friend, I must remind you.

105
00:06:59,619 --> 00:07:03,120
- You're getting older. Take it easy on that.
- You're just...

106
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,799
Hello, Principal Jin.

107
00:07:08,940 --> 00:07:13,179
There's not enough room here! I'm getting braver after each battle! Let's go to the sports field!

108
00:07:13,179 --> 00:07:15,339
However, my studies are very important!

109
00:07:15,339 --> 00:07:17,139
- Stop right there!
- Dad.

110
00:07:17,139 --> 00:07:19,900
- Call me Principal Jin.
- Principal Jin.

111
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:21,920
What is this?

112
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:25,279
What are you wearing? Roll down your pants.

113
00:07:29,620 --> 00:07:30,979
Where are you going?

114
00:07:30,979 --> 00:07:32,140
To get some fresh air.

115
00:07:32,140 --> 00:07:35,799
I can hear your shouting even from the other side of the mountain. Why are you involved in everything?

116
00:07:35,799 --> 00:07:38,700
What does their competition have to do with you?

117
00:07:38,700 --> 00:07:42,219
I just want to cheer for my friends.

118
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:46,979
Mi Jia, focus on your training.

119
00:07:47,539 --> 00:07:50,720
Tian Meng, focus on your studies.

120
00:07:51,339 --> 00:07:55,139
Jiabao, focus on your music.

121
00:07:55,139 --> 00:07:56,460
Okay.

122
00:07:56,460 --> 00:08:00,800
Can the three of you not join her in this mess?

123
00:08:08,730 --> 00:08:10,779
Don't practice anymore.

124
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:25,779
Let's go!

125
00:08:27,330 --> 00:08:30,299
Sis, eat, eat. Eat.

126
00:08:30,299 --> 00:08:32,299
Jin Doudou!

127
00:08:32,299 --> 00:08:34,159
Who told you to come to my room?

128
00:08:34,159 --> 00:08:37,120
Sis, want some carrot?

129
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:38,760
Good boy.

130
00:08:44,639 --> 00:08:47,539
"Brought together by misfortune,

131
00:08:47,539 --> 00:08:52,179
it doesn't matter if we know each other or not."
(T/N: reference to a poem from the Tang dynasty)

132
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:04,720
[Missing Persons Notice]

133
00:09:10,220 --> 00:09:13,400
Strawberries, your favorite.

134
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:16,380
They are really big and really sweet. Have some.

135
00:09:16,380 --> 00:09:18,180
Thank you, Auntie.

136
00:09:18,180 --> 00:09:23,539
Don't mention it. I have to thank you for keeping me company.

137
00:09:23,539 --> 00:09:27,640
I have no regrets in life now that I've found you.

138
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,879
Does it taste good?

139
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:32,079
You should have some too, Auntie.

140
00:09:33,860 --> 00:09:38,460
You should eat more.

141
00:09:44,450 --> 00:09:45,539
Where's Dawei?

142
00:09:45,539 --> 00:09:46,720
He went home to study.

143
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:48,259
Study?

144
00:09:48,259 --> 00:09:51,539
He said he was going to study. Study what? He's just sad.

145
00:09:51,539 --> 00:09:54,139
Wanwan likes someone else.

146
00:09:54,139 --> 00:09:56,120
Ye Xiaowen?

147
00:09:56,120 --> 00:10:00,600
I heard that boy has pretty good grades. Both of them got into the elite class.

148
00:10:04,980 --> 00:10:08,339
Should we teach that boy a lesson for Dawei?

149
00:10:08,339 --> 00:10:12,319
Forget it. That's Ye Xiaowen. Just the two of us?

150
00:10:12,319 --> 00:10:14,519
Just play your pool.

151
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:21,439
I...

152
00:10:21,439 --> 00:10:22,799
Dazhang.

153
00:10:22,799 --> 00:10:30,359
After all, Dawei is upset about that?

154
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:45,900
One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

155
00:10:45,900 --> 00:10:49,539
Two, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight.

156
00:10:49,539 --> 00:10:54,579
Three, two, three, four, five, six, seven, done!

157
00:10:54,579 --> 00:10:56,859
Are you crazy?

158
00:10:56,859 --> 00:10:58,740
What do you think? Have I improved?

159
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:02,440
Improved on what? You've been practicing for two weeks and you haven't made any progress!

160
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:05,579
Geez. Go home and dance to yourself.

161
00:11:05,579 --> 00:11:08,380
How am I supposed to do that when my dad's home?

162
00:11:08,380 --> 00:11:13,059
Besides, if I dance at home, your ceiling would creak.

163
00:11:13,059 --> 00:11:18,240
Have you ever considered this? Wouldn't it be even louder when you dance in front of us?

164
00:11:22,050 --> 00:11:24,779
Gao Yang, I have to give you a piece of my mind.

165
00:11:24,779 --> 00:11:27,240
Xiaowen and Mi Jia are going to compete soon.

166
00:11:27,240 --> 00:11:31,079
I'm practicing my dance moves all day while you're playing checkers all day.

167
00:11:31,079 --> 00:11:33,740
Besides, can't I dance at your place?

168
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:37,399
Can't I play checkers? I'm helping our athlete relax

169
00:11:37,399 --> 00:11:40,021
If he doesn't have a good mentality, how would he compete?

170
00:11:43,620 --> 00:11:47,099
But I'm competing against Niu Wanwan tomorrow.

171
00:11:47,099 --> 00:11:50,079
Who's going to do it if I don't?

172
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:52,800
It's your turn.

173
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,800
How's that?

174
00:12:06,170 --> 00:12:08,980
Why isn't Jin Beibei here yet?

175
00:12:09,930 --> 00:12:11,260
She's scared.

176
00:12:11,260 --> 00:12:13,459
Who's scared?

177
00:12:36,770 --> 00:12:41,159
- What are you looking at?
- So what if I'm looking at you? Just get to it.

178
00:12:41,159 --> 00:12:43,279
Not me.

179
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:45,820
Come on.

180
00:12:50,900 --> 00:12:53,419
Gao Yang, hurry.

181
00:12:53,419 --> 00:12:54,919
Hurry.

182
00:12:58,690 --> 00:12:59,900
Beibei, you should dance.

183
00:12:59,900 --> 00:13:02,220
What are you talking about? It's your turn. Hurry up.

184
00:13:02,220 --> 00:13:04,040
Why don't we just forget it?

185
00:13:09,620 --> 00:13:12,679
That's right. Breath. Adjust your breathing.

186
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,120
That's right.

187
00:13:39,120 --> 00:13:42,260
Turn, turn, stop.

188
00:13:57,740 --> 00:14:12,319
Gao Yang! Gao Yang!

189
00:14:12,319 --> 00:14:14,679
Don't go!

190
00:14:16,159 --> 00:14:18,399
Gao Yang!

191
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:20,959
Cheers!

192
00:14:20,959 --> 00:14:25,500
Congratulations to Gao Yang for winning the privilege to lead!

193
00:14:25,500 --> 00:14:29,559
You're as excellent as your female teammates. You are more coquettish than girls.

194
00:14:29,559 --> 00:14:34,039
Gao Yang, tell us the truth, you did such a good job dancing. Did you secretly watch me dance and steal my moves?

195
00:14:34,039 --> 00:14:35,740
I'm just born with an innate talent.

196
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:38,240
Gao Yang is such...

197
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:43,540
such...

198
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:44,780
Such a good dancer!

199
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:47,520
Such a good dancer!

200
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:49,159
Applaud!

201
00:14:50,340 --> 00:14:53,079
It's too early to celebrate.

202
00:14:53,079 --> 00:14:56,900
- After Xiaowen and Mi Jia win first place, we will celebrate then!
- Yes, yes!

203
00:14:56,900 --> 00:14:58,839
- Come on, let's eat.
- Let's eat.

204
00:14:58,839 --> 00:15:01,020
Jia, eat more meat. Have another piece.

205
00:15:01,020 --> 00:15:02,419
Xiaowen, eat some meat.

206
00:15:02,419 --> 00:15:04,620
- Chicken feet, it's full of collagen.
- I'll eat vegetables.

207
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:07,400
There's a chicken wing too. Have another piece.

208
00:15:07,400 --> 00:15:10,459
Beibei, stop stuffing Mi Jia with food.

209
00:15:10,459 --> 00:15:13,140
She has to compete tomorrow. She needs nutrients.

210
00:15:13,140 --> 00:15:17,336
That's why she has to stay away from greasy foods. What if she has diarrhea tomorrow?

211
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:20,320
Listen to Xiaowen.

212
00:15:21,530 --> 00:15:23,739
Let's change plates then.

213
00:15:23,739 --> 00:15:26,860
Bear with it, Jia. You can eat these after the competition.

214
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:30,380
Plus, I've prepared a mysterious gift for you.

215
00:15:30,380 --> 00:15:31,539
What mysterious gift?

216
00:15:31,539 --> 00:15:33,399
I'm not telling you.

217
00:15:34,980 --> 00:15:36,419
Fine, don't tell me.

218
00:15:36,419 --> 00:15:39,419
Anyway, I prepared a mysterious gift for Xiaowen too.

219
00:15:39,419 --> 00:15:41,100
Mine is definitely better than yours.

220
00:15:41,100 --> 00:15:43,699
That's not possible. How can you beat me?

221
00:15:43,699 --> 00:15:49,220
I'm going to take Mi Jia to see "Super Girl" live!
(T/N: A Chinese singing contest for female contestants)

222
00:15:51,170 --> 00:15:53,199
- You can't beat that, can you?
- I can't beat that.

223
00:15:53,199 --> 00:15:55,340
Beibei, thank you.

224
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:57,459
You're welcome. You'll know when you get there.

225
00:15:57,459 --> 00:16:00,479
The live-show would definitely be full of surprises!

226
00:16:01,170 --> 00:16:02,260
Oh, God.

227
00:16:02,260 --> 00:16:04,900
Why did I reveal it?

228
00:16:05,930 --> 00:16:08,740
Gao Yang, it's all your fault!

229
00:16:11,930 --> 00:16:14,040
What's your gift then?

230
00:16:14,040 --> 00:16:16,259
I can't tell you.

231
00:16:16,259 --> 00:16:18,820
You! You don't get to eat!

232
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,919
- Let go.
- No!

233
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:23,200
Let's eat in peace.

234
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:25,019
You two!

235
00:16:37,020 --> 00:16:40,179
Xiaowen, do you want to see "Super Girl" live? I'll go with you.

236
00:16:40,179 --> 00:16:41,260
No.

237
00:16:41,260 --> 00:16:43,139
I knew you didn't like that.

238
00:16:43,139 --> 00:16:46,740
Check this out. What do you think?

239
00:16:48,190 --> 00:16:51,200
- What is this?
- The new shoes I bought for you.

240
00:16:51,200 --> 00:16:52,240
I don't need it.

241
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:55,659
Look at your shoes. They are too worn out. You can't wear them anymore.

242
00:16:55,659 --> 00:16:58,859
They'll look new after I polish them. I can still wear them. Don't waste your money.

243
00:16:58,859 --> 00:17:02,179
Stop polishing it. Look, you've worn it for a long time.

244
00:17:02,179 --> 00:17:05,620
The glue is coming apart. The sole is almost worn out.

245
00:17:06,820 --> 00:17:09,500
Let me tell you, just put on these new shoes.

246
00:17:09,500 --> 00:17:12,580
There's something particular about them. It's high-tech.

247
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:16,960
These all-around air cushions are specially designed for runners.

248
00:17:16,960 --> 00:17:20,259
They will protect your feet and your ankles against any harm.

249
00:17:20,259 --> 00:17:23,240
I shopped in Piao Jiutong's store for hours to buy them for you.

250
00:17:23,240 --> 00:17:25,820
I told you I don't need them. Don't waste your money.

251
00:17:25,820 --> 00:17:28,659
Just put them on. Why are you being so difficult?

252
00:17:28,659 --> 00:17:31,399
You can win first place if you wear them.

253
00:17:31,399 --> 00:17:32,980
Besides,

254
00:17:34,490 --> 00:17:36,579
I already bought them.

255
00:17:36,579 --> 00:17:39,480
It's only a waste if you don't wear them,

256
00:17:40,250 --> 00:17:41,759
right?

257
00:17:47,360 --> 00:17:51,750
By the way, remember to cut the tag off. Go to bed earlier tonight.

258
00:17:51,750 --> 00:17:53,640
Good luck with the competition tomorrow.

259
00:17:53,640 --> 00:17:56,519
I'll be waiting for you by the finish line.

260
00:17:57,760 --> 00:17:59,939
♪ Sing whenever you want ♪

261
00:17:59,939 --> 00:18:03,240
♪ Sing it loud and proud ♪

262
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:06,940
♪ You'll be at center stage ♪

263
00:18:33,380 --> 00:18:36,459
Are these new shoes?

264
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:41,000
There are wrinkles on them.

265
00:18:44,100 --> 00:18:46,440
They don't smell.

266
00:18:51,490 --> 00:18:55,599
Tell me, why did you come to me so late at night?

267
00:18:58,690 --> 00:19:00,499
I...

268
00:19:03,060 --> 00:19:06,419
Just be out with it or go home.

269
00:19:06,419 --> 00:19:08,319
Dazhang came to us.

270
00:19:08,319 --> 00:19:09,340
What did he want?

271
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:14,399
We told him Wanwan fell for Ye Xiaowen and ditched you.

272
00:19:14,399 --> 00:19:16,580
Why did tell him that?

273
00:19:16,580 --> 00:19:20,059
No, it was mainly because Dazhang forced it out of us. We wouldn't dare say no to him.

274
00:19:20,059 --> 00:19:21,219
What did he say?

275
00:19:21,219 --> 00:19:27,020
Nothing. He just said he knows why you're upset now and he wants to help you.

276
00:19:28,120 --> 00:19:32,819
Dawei, do you think Dazhang would do something bad?

277
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:35,580
[Tieyuan City High School Long Distance Running Competition]

278
00:19:35,580 --> 00:19:36,780
[Anticipate the Olympics 2005]

279
00:19:36,780 --> 00:19:38,590
[Tieyuan City High School Long Distance Running Competition]

280
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:41,999
Students, in 2008,

281
00:19:41,999 --> 00:19:45,279
Beijing will be hosting the Olympic Games.

282
00:19:45,279 --> 00:19:48,799
In the spirit of anticipating the Olympic Games,

283
00:19:48,799 --> 00:19:54,120
our Tieyuan High School Long-Distance Race is about to begin.

284
00:19:54,120 --> 00:19:56,870
As a representative of our faculty,

285
00:19:56,870 --> 00:20:00,660
I wish everyone will demonstrate their character

286
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:02,200
and style during the competition.

287
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:05,280
Friendship comes first, competition comes second.

288
00:20:05,280 --> 00:20:08,860
I wish you all the best.

289
00:20:08,860 --> 00:20:11,160
Go, Xiaowen!

290
00:20:11,160 --> 00:20:12,940
Go for it!

291
00:20:21,100 --> 00:20:24,000
Xiaowen, you're wearing new sneakers?

292
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:26,039
Did Mr. Gao buy them for you?

293
00:20:26,960 --> 00:20:31,440
I'm wearing new shoes too. Auntie bought them for me. Do they look nice?

294
00:20:32,499 --> 00:20:33,839
Ready, go!

295
00:20:33,839 --> 00:20:37,460
No.3 High School, success all the way!

296
00:20:37,460 --> 00:20:41,660
Mi Jia, Xiao Wen, always the best!

297
00:20:44,870 --> 00:20:47,959
No.2 High School, bound to succeed!

298
00:20:47,959 --> 00:20:52,440
Sizhe leaves no opponent undefeated!
[Sizhe is the best in Tieyuan]

299
00:20:56,100 --> 00:20:57,599
Come on, Tian Meng, top them!

300
00:20:57,599 --> 00:20:58,820
Meng, top them!

301
00:20:58,820 --> 00:21:03,259
"Ride the wind and waves, Sail straight to the sea!"
(T/N: reference to a poem from the Tang Dynasty)

302
00:21:03,259 --> 00:21:05,259
No, no, that's too literary! Do another one!

303
00:21:05,259 --> 00:21:06,400
Hurry, Sea of Knowledge.

304
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:09,860
"The ocean is boundless for fish to leap. The sky is unlimited for birds to fly."
(T/N: reference to "Journey to the West")

305
00:21:09,860 --> 00:21:11,639
No, no. Let me do it!

306
00:21:11,639 --> 00:21:17,599
Xiaowen is here! You better be humble! Don't applaud! Just scream!

307
00:21:17,599 --> 00:21:21,799
Go, Xiaowen!

308
00:21:23,699 --> 00:21:27,780
Go get them!

309
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:32,699
Athletes, on your mark!

310
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,080
Ready.

311
00:21:36,080 --> 00:21:40,799
Go, go, go!
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

312
00:21:40,799 --> 00:21:49,260
Go, Mi Jia, go! Go, Xiaowen, go!
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

313
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:55,500
♫ Starlight shines along the way ♫

314
00:21:55,500 --> 00:22:01,440
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

315
00:22:01,440 --> 00:22:07,890
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

316
00:22:07,890 --> 00:22:16,130
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

317
00:22:16,130 --> 00:22:19,199
You've been studying really hard lately.

318
00:22:19,199 --> 00:22:22,720
I want to get into college sooner to get away from you.

319
00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,000
Good.

320
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:29,559
If you have that kind of ambition, you'll have a promising future.

321
00:22:29,559 --> 00:22:31,100
That's about it.

322
00:22:31,100 --> 00:22:35,780
You have to study hard. Our entire family is counting on you.

323
00:22:43,930 --> 00:22:46,680
- Where are you going?
- To watch the competition.

324
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:47,799
Competition?

325
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:50,580
Isn't the city hosting a long-distance race?

326
00:22:50,580 --> 00:22:52,440
Isn't your school participating too?

327
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:55,540
It's perfect. I'll go visit Bin and have a chat with him.

328
00:22:55,540 --> 00:23:00,480
By the way, Mr. Gao told me that Xiaowen is participating in the competition too.

329
00:23:00,480 --> 00:23:02,100
Are you close with Xiaowen?

330
00:23:02,100 --> 00:23:06,080
Can he win first place? Is he good enough?

331
00:23:10,650 --> 00:23:14,860
What are you doing? I was just praising you. Why did you run away again?

332
00:23:14,860 --> 00:23:18,440
I wonder how they're doing now. Who's in the lead?

333
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:21,860
Exactly, they didn't put up a livestream or anything.

334
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:27,759
You guys wait here. I'm going to the restroom.

335
00:23:27,759 --> 00:23:30,140
- Go on.
- Take a stroll.

336
00:23:39,459 --> 00:23:42,119
Why are you sitting here? How about this?

337
00:23:42,119 --> 00:23:46,639
Since you came with a bike, go check on how they are doing. Come back and tell us.

338
00:23:46,639 --> 00:23:48,580
All right. Wait for me. Here.

339
00:23:48,580 --> 00:23:51,199
- Be careful.
- Wait for me.

340
00:23:52,100 --> 00:23:53,600
Set off.

341
00:24:00,250 --> 00:24:02,820
Go, Xiaowen!

342
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:05,300
Make sure your number plate is secured! You won't get a score if you lose it!

343
00:24:05,300 --> 00:24:08,640
Go for it!

344
00:24:10,780 --> 00:24:13,200
He should be a shoo-in for the first place.

345
00:24:13,200 --> 00:24:16,160
Do you see the first place? He's my student.

346
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:24,099
Mi Jia! Go for it!

347
00:24:24,099 --> 00:24:25,800
Go for it!

348
00:24:26,699 --> 00:24:28,860
Go for it!

349
00:24:33,160 --> 00:24:36,060
Two champions for sure.

350
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:43,299
Sir, have you seen Dazhang?

351
00:24:43,299 --> 00:24:45,400
- He went to watch the race.
- The long-distance race?

352
00:24:45,400 --> 00:24:47,140
I think so.

353
00:24:55,470 --> 00:24:58,879
Go for it!

354
00:25:10,540 --> 00:25:14,500
What's Ye Xiaowen's number? Did you find out yet?

355
00:25:15,599 --> 00:25:16,699
Dazhang is rushing us again.

356
00:25:16,699 --> 00:25:19,580
What's the point of rushing us? He just gave us a name. How should we find him?

357
00:25:19,580 --> 00:25:20,900
All right, let's ask around.

358
00:25:20,900 --> 00:25:22,400
Go ask.

359
00:25:25,280 --> 00:25:27,959
- Hello, Girls. Do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?
- I don't know.

360
00:25:27,959 --> 00:25:30,000
- Do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?
- No.

361
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:33,600
- Hello, Girl. Do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?
- No.

362
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:38,960
- Excuse me, do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?
- I don't know.

363
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,619
No.

364
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:45,400
- Do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?
- Do you know Ye Xiaowen's number?

365
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,720
Hey, Sir.

366
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:49,339
- Sir, I know.
- You know?

367
00:25:49,339 --> 00:25:50,219
Why are you asking for him?

368
00:25:50,219 --> 00:25:52,540
- We're his fans.
- His fans.

369
00:25:52,540 --> 00:25:53,839
You have great taste.

370
00:25:53,839 --> 00:25:57,220
Let me tell you, No. 2021, he's definitely the champion.

371
00:25:57,220 --> 00:25:59,320
- No. 2021?
- Let's go.

372
00:25:59,320 --> 00:26:03,580
Wait, where are you going? He's about to be at the finish line. Why don't you just wait there?

373
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:06,799
- We want to take some pictures of him during the race.
- That's right.

374
00:26:06,799 --> 00:26:09,559
Photos of the race. I know a place. Come with me.

375
00:26:09,559 --> 00:26:11,739
Bro, we have the bike. Get on the bike!

376
00:26:11,739 --> 00:26:13,459
- You have a bike?
- Get on the bike.

377
00:26:13,459 --> 00:26:16,919
- The bike is so cool!
- Come on, get on the bike.

378
00:26:18,140 --> 00:26:19,840
Let's turn around.

379
00:26:24,730 --> 00:26:27,220
- Have you seen Ye Xiaowen?
- No.

380
00:26:27,220 --> 00:26:29,300
Have you seen Ye Xiaowen?

381
00:26:34,210 --> 00:26:36,119
Have you seen Ye Xiaowen?

382
00:26:36,119 --> 00:26:38,660
- What... what's wrong?
- Where is he?

383
00:26:38,660 --> 00:26:41,659
- He... he ran out.
- Where did he go?

384
00:27:01,100 --> 00:27:04,559
We're almost there. It's right in front of us. O-Over there.

385
00:27:04,559 --> 00:27:07,660
- Over there?
- That's right. Next to that tree. Exactly.

386
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:09,359
Here it is.

387
00:27:09,359 --> 00:27:10,859
Okay.

388
00:27:17,030 --> 00:27:19,419
Let me tell you, this is the best place to watch it.

389
00:27:19,419 --> 00:27:21,219
In a little while, see that?

390
00:27:21,219 --> 00:27:23,580
- Over there?
- Yes, yes. The athletes will make a turn...

391
00:27:23,580 --> 00:27:27,339
Thanks, Buddy. You're so kind. Just come to me if you need anything in the future.

392
00:27:27,339 --> 00:27:29,800
- Not at all.
- Thank you.

393
00:27:29,800 --> 00:27:32,280
Don't mention it.

394
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:34,259
Anyone who supports Xiaowen is my friend.

395
00:27:34,259 --> 00:27:35,759
- Okay.
- Well, I'll be on my way then.

396
00:27:35,759 --> 00:27:37,559
Well, take some nice photos. Make him look handsome.

397
00:27:37,559 --> 00:27:39,300
- Sure, okay. Bye.
- Bye, bye.

398
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:40,659
The bike is so cool.

399
00:27:40,659 --> 00:27:42,359
That's for sure.

400
00:27:55,340 --> 00:27:57,140
Go on.

401
00:27:57,140 --> 00:27:59,319
You found him?

402
00:27:59,319 --> 00:28:01,620
Good. Wait for me.

403
00:28:03,259 --> 00:28:08,800
♪ Run with the wind, freedom is my direction ♪

404
00:28:08,800 --> 00:28:10,700
What's wrong, Jiabao?

405
00:28:12,970 --> 00:28:14,100
What happened?

406
00:28:14,100 --> 00:28:16,739
Dong Dawei is here. He's looking everywhere for Xiaowen.

407
00:28:16,739 --> 00:28:18,639
Why is he looking for Xiaowen?

408
00:28:18,639 --> 00:28:22,219
I don't know. He seems really anxious.

409
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:28,520
Go, go! Go find the teacher! Hurry up!

410
00:28:58,450 --> 00:29:00,319
Give me my number plate back!

411
00:29:05,780 --> 00:29:07,819
- Come on!
- Give me my number plate back!

412
00:29:07,819 --> 00:29:09,380
Come on!

413
00:29:14,210 --> 00:29:16,279
Give me my number plate back!

414
00:29:23,900 --> 00:29:26,259
You're Ye Xiaowen?

415
00:29:27,170 --> 00:29:30,940
Do you now Dong Dawei? He's my little brother.

416
00:29:31,620 --> 00:29:34,859
I came here today to give you a message from him.

417
00:29:34,859 --> 00:29:37,720
Stay away from his woman.

418
00:29:37,759 --> 00:29:39,599
Can you do that?

419
00:29:50,100 --> 00:29:53,380
Do you understand what my boss just said?

420
00:29:53,380 --> 00:29:56,720
Behave or it's gonna hurt!

421
00:29:58,739 --> 00:29:59,939
Dazhang.

422
00:30:04,759 --> 00:30:09,039
What are you doing, Little B*stard? How dare you get involved in this?

423
00:30:09,039 --> 00:30:12,480
I'm not getting involved. I'm just passing by on my way home.

424
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:15,340
Well, take another path home.

425
00:30:15,340 --> 00:30:16,459
I'll take another path.

426
00:30:16,459 --> 00:30:20,039
Boss, don't let him leave!

427
00:30:20,039 --> 00:30:24,340
No, no! Look at how nice your boss is. You should work for a boss like that. Well...

428
00:30:24,340 --> 00:30:25,860
Boss!

429
00:30:25,860 --> 00:30:27,820
Stop! Stop right there!

430
00:30:27,820 --> 00:30:29,960
Hurry, you run first!

431
00:30:31,039 --> 00:30:34,159
- What about you?
- Don't mind me. Go get the champion!

432
00:30:36,179 --> 00:30:38,499
Are you going to college or not?

433
00:30:40,100 --> 00:30:41,800
Stop!

434
00:30:44,110 --> 00:30:45,860
Stop!

435
00:30:45,860 --> 00:30:47,760
Don't move!

436
00:31:36,300 --> 00:31:38,880
♫ The white city ♫

437
00:31:38,880 --> 00:31:42,820
♫ The gray wallpaper ♫

438
00:31:42,820 --> 00:31:49,680
♫ The night sky after shooting stars have left ♫

439
00:31:50,670 --> 00:31:57,380
♫ The warm shadows fading in the night ♫

440
00:31:57,380 --> 00:32:04,320
♫ We laugh and ramble about our future so many interesting things♫

441
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:11,740
♫ The wasted times we went through together ♫

442
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:18,660
♫ Nobody else was there, only us and that's why it's so beautiful ♫

443
00:32:19,710 --> 00:32:25,250
♫ If you were to ask me where my future would be ♫

444
00:32:25,850 --> 00:32:28,900
♫ How much courage it would take ♫

445
00:32:28,900 --> 00:32:33,320
♫ To live in the same city with you ♫

446
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:38,540
Hurry, you run first!

447
00:32:38,540 --> 00:32:41,159
- What about you?
- Don't mind me. Go get the champion!

448
00:32:41,159 --> 00:32:43,499
Are you going to college or not?

449
00:32:45,860 --> 00:32:51,699
Xiaowen, I can share your responsibility. What's mine is yours.

450
00:32:51,699 --> 00:32:53,620
I'll share my allowance with you now.

451
00:32:53,620 --> 00:32:57,979
When I make money in the future, I'll give you half of my salary too. I mean what I said.

452
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:04,259
I know I'm really childish now. I'm really unreliable too.

453
00:33:04,259 --> 00:33:07,219
But I will become very reliable one day.

454
00:33:07,219 --> 00:33:09,219
I mean it.

455
00:33:10,693 --> 00:33:16,070
♫ I live at an address that never existed ♫

456
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:24,358
♫ Like the beginning of a time warp ♫

457
00:33:24,358 --> 00:33:30,550
♫ Confusing the unknown, the moment, and the lifetime ♫

458
00:33:30,550 --> 00:33:34,075
♫ Ripples of memories ♫

459
00:33:34,075 --> 00:33:39,100
♫ Say the wind blew here once ♫

460
00:33:39,100 --> 00:33:45,225
♫ It is a house I have never visited ♫

461
00:33:45,225 --> 00:33:53,408
♫ But it left me with a lot of luxuries ♫

462
00:33:53,408 --> 00:34:00,033
♫ All the nostalgia only lasts for a moment ♫

463
00:34:00,033 --> 00:34:01,800
What do you think?

464
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:03,340
These are the new shoes I bought you.

465
00:34:03,340 --> 00:34:06,039
You can win the first place when you wear them.

466
00:34:25,019 --> 00:34:27,060
I don't want to trouble anyone.

467
00:34:27,060 --> 00:34:29,680
Aren't you troubling me now?

468
00:34:33,380 --> 00:34:36,540
Rely on your siblings at home and rely on your friends outside.

469
00:34:36,540 --> 00:34:39,620
Ye Xiaowen, are we friends?

470
00:34:39,620 --> 00:34:42,960
Friends are not important to me. I only care about the competition now. I want to win.

471
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:44,979
I'm counting on this to go to college, understand?

472
00:34:44,979 --> 00:34:46,300
What am I to you?

473
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:47,900
A roommate.

474
00:34:51,090 --> 00:34:53,180
I'm your roommate?

475
00:34:55,530 --> 00:35:01,220
Roommate, sorry for disturbing you. From now on, I will never bother you again.

476
00:35:12,490 --> 00:35:15,240
Hey, that athlete, you're running in the wrong direction!

477
00:36:20,100 --> 00:36:26,370
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

478
00:36:26,370 --> 00:36:33,340
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

479
00:36:33,340 --> 00:36:39,630
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

480
00:36:39,630 --> 00:36:45,670
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

481
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:52,220
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

482
00:36:52,220 --> 00:36:57,960
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

483
00:36:57,960 --> 00:37:01,770
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

484
00:37:01,770 --> 00:37:05,190
♫ Set sail for your dreams ♫

485
00:37:05,190 --> 00:37:08,490
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

486
00:37:08,490 --> 00:37:13,150
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

487
00:37:13,150 --> 00:37:15,260
♫ I'll be there for you ♫

488
00:37:15,260 --> 00:37:18,460
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

489
00:37:18,460 --> 00:37:22,670
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

490
00:37:22,670 --> 00:37:26,490
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

491
00:37:26,490 --> 00:37:34,450
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫

